Release Information

The IDA Disassembler and Debugger is an
interactive, programmable, extendible
multi-processor disassembler hosted on Windows
Linux, or Mac OS X. IDA has become the de-facto
standard for the analysis of hostile code
vulnerability research and COTS validation
